Metadata: Novel sponge-derived amino acids. 12. Tryptophan-​derived pigments and accompanying sesterterpenes from "Fascaplysinopi​s reticulata"

This paper reports the bioactive constituents of the sponge "Fascaplysinops​is reticulata", collected from the Benga Lagoon of the Fiji islands. The comprehensive study involved four separate Fijian collections, and its very complex mixtures consisted of sesterterpenes, alkaloids, and alkaloid-​sesterterpene salts. Several new compounds are described.
